io.doov.core

Interface FieldModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DslModel, Iterable<Map.Entry<FieldId,Object>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseFieldModel

    public interface FieldModel
extends Iterable<Map.Entry<FieldId,Object>>, DslModel
    An model that maps FieldId to values. Each FieldId can map to at most one value.
